Some Commonwealth nationals came to the UK as:
Students but could not continue to renew their visas due to the hostile immigration rules;
Spouses whose marriages did not work but could not return having sacrificed everything in their countries;
Individuals who left their countries at very young ages but cannot qualify under the immigration rules because they are single;
Minors who cant renew their visas because their parents are overstayers and they do not qualify under the immigration rules
